channel.title: Are accounts worth any $$ these days?
channel.description: I've got a real old account that has decent RS2 stats, but good RSC stats (99 att, 99 str, 1 def). Seeing as Jagex have just re-opened RSC to the public, I was wondering if this acc has any worth to it? Just curious, don't think i'd sell, just food for thought.
